                ul(class="mt40")
                    li 
                        strong.u-textColor_3 Man: 
                        |   Would you rather stay home or go out tonight?
                    li(class="mt20")
                        strong.u-textColor_3 Woman:
                        |   I'd rather go out. I am a little bit tired, but I don't want to stay home. We usually stay home on Friday nights, so we could go out tonight for a change. What about you? Would you rather stay in or go out?
                
                    li(class="mt20")
                        strong.u-textColor_3 Man: 
                        |   I would prefer to stay in, but you're right. We usually stay home so we can go out if you want.
                    
                    li(class="mt20")
                        strong.u-textColor_3 Woman:
                        |  That would be nice. What do you feel like doing?
                    
                    li(class="mt20")
                        strong.u-textColor_3 Man:
                        |   I'd prefer to go somewhere quiet. Where we can talk and maybe have a light dinner and some drinks.
                    
                    li(class="mt20")
                        strong.u-textColor_3 Woman:
                        |   Really? Not me. I would rather go somewhere fun, maybe even with some live music.
                    
                    li(class="mt20")
                        strong.u-textColor_3 Man:
                        |  But I thought you were tired! Do you really want to go somewhere loud?
                    
                    li(class="mt20")
                        strong.u-textColor_3 Woman: 
                        |  I am, but not too tired to have some fun.

                    li(class="mt20")
                        strong.u-textColor_3 Man:
                        |  Well, I'd prefer not to, but... OK. Let's find a place with a nice live band.



